description: Have mom help you put the cookies in the oven
Put the body and head together
Get the milk out of the fridge
Load the dirty dishes into the dishwasher
Put one cup behind each plate
Put silverware next to each plate
Pour the cereal into the bowl
Pour the milk into the bowl
Put the cookies on the baking sheet
Put the milk back in the fridge and close the fridge
put soap on hands with bar of soap
Put dishwasher soap in the dishwasher
Take the cookies out of the oven
Turn on water and rinse hands
Pour a little circle of batter onto the pan and cook for 3 minutes
Flip the circle and cook until it is lightly golden
